Azure Storage redundancy ensures data durability and availability by replicating data.

Options include:

* LRS
* ZRS
* GRS
* RA-GRS

For example, data is replicated across multiple locations.

# Real-Life Use Case:
A real-life use case is disaster recovery planning.

# Real-Life Example;
Another example is ensuring availability during outages.

Redundancy protects against data loss.
